        "TileImage": "$($repository ef5793ad-d069-46e7-9cbf-6fc355ded2bc).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Your targets are Antonio Delacruz, known as Professor Antonio, and Torres Piombo. Delacruz and Piombo control all the drug trafficking in Sapienza and its surroundings. Delacruz is the chemist, and Piombo is the dealer. Our client, a major European cartel looking to enter the Sapienza market, knows they won’t succeed with the competition from Delacruz, who produces a far superior drug and have the protection of the famous biochemist Silvio Caruso. You know what to do 47.",
